issue.title: Renaming the Repository

milestone.title: First Functional and Not Super Buggy Release!
milestone.description:
For this HackRU, which was my first hackathon and hX0rz's second hackathon, we started at around 11:00 and finished around 21:30.

This is our first actual project together and although our coding skills did not overlap, we managed to make something that we both didn't really know how to do.

We were inspired by a classmate in BU to try chrome extensions, and we did just that.

Shoutouts to that high school senior who says "duck" all the time, as he inspired us to do it for the kids, the kids who take the standardized tests.

issue.body: I think we did an okay job.
